jCUOqEK8Lln0PK3GeUl6IQ
copper star has a special place in my heart for sure. the atmosphere is perfect for a small meeting or for reading or studying. it is also very cool inside and is located in an area great for thrifting.   the coffee itself is good. their milk steaming ability isn't excellent, but they pull consistent shots. their chai is great and their sesame ginger tuna sandwich is actually outstanding.   since its opening, i have probably visited copper star more frequently than any other coffee shop in phoenix.

