I go here regularly because they make the best Ethiopian food I have ever had and because the people who work at Gojo are super genuine and kind. The vegetarian options are consistently awesome. The atmosphere is great and would be good for a party, a meeting, a show, or anything. Even has a good spiritual vibe, long may Ethiopia reign with peace, justice & love. I recommend Gojo and the Ethiopian cafe in the same plaza to everyone.

